341367809.name: Sun & Moon—Team Up
341367809.description: TAG TEAM Pokémon-GX are here, brand-new cards that feature paired-up and powered-up Pokémon! The Pokémon TCG: Sun & Moon—Team Up expansion offers amazing battle teams like Pikachu & Zekrom-GX, Eevee & Snorlax-GX, and Gengar & Mimikyu-GX, plus even more Pokémon-GX: Lycanroc-GX, Hoopa-GX, Cobalion-GX, and others! When the teams put their moves into motion, it’s a total free-for-all. Check out the awesome action and dynamic duos in the Sun & Moon—Team Up expansion!

SM9RelentlessFlameBundle.name: Relentless Flame
SM9RelentlessFlameBundle.description: Fire it up with the relentless flames of Charizard! This deck burns super hot, so keep feeding Charizard enough Fire Energy to create an unstoppable Continuous Blaze Ball. Burn bright and burn true with the Relentless Flame theme deck!

SM9RelentlessFlamePCD.name: Relentless Flame
SM9RelentlessFlamePCD.description: Fire it up with the relentless flames of Charizard! This deck burns super hot, so keep feeding Charizard enough Fire Energy to create an unstoppable Continuous Blaze Ball. Burn bright and burn true with the Relentless Flame theme deck!

SM9TorrentialCannonBundle.name: Torrential Cannon
SM9TorrentialCannonBundle.description: Give your opponent a high-pressure soaking with help from Blastoise! Use Golduck’s Amnesia to keep the other side off-balance as you power up a devastating Hydro Tackle attack. Wash away the competition with the Torrential Cannon theme deck!

SM9TorrentialCannonPCD.name: Torrential Cannon
SM9TorrentialCannonPCD.description: Give your opponent a high-pressure soaking with help from Blastoise! Use Golduck’s Amnesia to keep the other side off-balance as you power up a devastating Hydro Tackle attack. Wash away the competition with the Torrential Cannon theme deck!

Sp19TinCelebiVenusaurGXBundle.name: Celebi & Venusaur-GX Deck
Sp19TinCelebiVenusaurGXBundle.description: With Celebi & Venusaur-GX leading the way, this Grass-type deck brings Venusaur, Sceptile, and even Shuckle into the arena, plus great Trainer cards including Guzma, Lillie, Ultra Ball, and Ingo & Emmet!

Sp19TinEeveeSnorlaxGXBundle.name: Eevee & Snorlax-GX Deck
Sp19TinEeveeSnorlaxGXBundle.description: Come have fun with Eevee & Snorlax-GX surfing a Water-type wave, with help from Blastoise, Lapras, Brock’s Grit, Erika’s Hospitality—and two Double Colorless Energy! Their combination of freewheeling and hard-hitting makes this deck shine!

Sp19TinFlareonGXBundle.name: Flareon-GX Deck
Sp19TinFlareonGXBundle.description: With Flareon-GX and Blaziken firing up the attack, this Fire-type deck brings Moltres, Oranguru, and Magcargo into the ring of lava, plus great Trainer cards including Guzma, Kiawe, Ultra Ball, and Rescue Stretcher!

Sp19TinJolteonGXBundle.name: Jolteon-GX Deck
Sp19TinJolteonGXBundle.description: Throw up some major static with Jolteon-GX, Zebstrika, and Electivire, and boost their voltage with Electropower, Field Blower, and Volkner! Combine a zillion zaps and buzzes to leave your opponent in a state of shock with this Lightning-type deck!

Sp19TinPikachuZekromGXBundle.name: Pikachu & Zekrom-GX Deck
Sp19TinPikachuZekromGXBundle.description: Blast the lightning of Pikachu & Zekrom-GX and their friends from Magnezone to Kangaskhan, together with strong Trainer cards from Lillie to Guzma. This Lightning-type deck can call down the thunder on those opposing Pokémon!

Sp19TinVaporeonGXBundle.name: Vaporeon-GX Deck
Sp19TinVaporeonGXBundle.description: Freeze and frost those foes with Vaporeon-GX and its friends Alolan Ninetales, Quagsire, and Naganadel, together with strong Trainer cards such as Guzma, Judge, and Lillie. This Water-type deck is ready to roll in the tide!
